```dockerfile
# Builder stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jdk-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

# Copy Maven project files
COPY pom.xml .
COPY src/ src/

# Build the JAR
RUN apk add --no-cache maven && \
    mvn clean package -DskipTests && \
    mv target/*.jar app.jar

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team" \
      version="1.0" \
      description="Java analytics dashboard"

# Install dependencies for certificate management and fonts
RUN apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    ca-certificates && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

WORKDIR /app

# Import AWS RDS root CA certificate into Java truststore
RUN curl -s https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem -o /tmp/rds-ca-bundle.pem && \
    keytool -import -noprompt -trustcacerts -alias rds-ca-bundle \
    -file /tmp/rds-ca-bundle.pem \
    -keystore "$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts" \
    -storepass changeit && \
    rm /tmp/rds-ca-bundle.pem

# Import Azure DigiCert certificate into Java truststore
RUN curl -s https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt -o /tmp/digicert.crt && \
    keytool -import -noprompt -trustcacerts -alias digicert-global-root \
    -file /tmp/digicert.crt \
    -keystore "$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts" \
    -storepass changeit && \
    rm /tmp/digicert.crt

# Create non-root user
RUN addgroup -g 1001 appgroup && \
    adduser -D -u 1001 -G appgroup app

# Copy JAR from builder
COPY --from=builder --chown=app:appgroup /build/app.jar .

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
